lead_paragraph: Canada scored two late goals to claim a nervy 2-1 win over Team Europe and complete a series sweep of the World Cup of Hockey final on Thursday, confirming their status as the sport's undisputed superpower.

headline.print_headline: Canada Stage Late Comeback to Win World Cup
headline.main: Canada Stage Late Comeback to Win World Cup
